['Saja hai bhojanaalay, bhojan ka hai himaalay', '
Lagi hai bhuk jamake, khaaunga peth bharke', '
Saja hai bhojanaalay, bhojan ka hai himaalay', '
Lagi hai bhuk jamake, khaaunga peth bharke', 'Laddu laal pedha imarti naankataayi', '
Bundi son halawa rasgulla rasmalaayi', '
Kaala gulaabjaamun wa ha ha ha, khaaunga peth bharke', '
Saja hai bhojanaalay, bhojan ka hai himaalay', '
Lagi hai bhuk jamake, khaaunga peth bharke', '
Wa ha ha ha', 'Puri sabji chatani, aur ghee mein duba halawa', '
Dudh ki nadi hai, khir ka hai jalawa', '
Khana hai lajawab wa ha ha ha, khaaunga peth bharke', '
Saja hai bhojanaalay, bhojan ka hai himaalay', '
Lagi hai bhuk jamake, khaaunga peth bharke', '
Wa ha ha ha', 'Ped mithe mithe, phal ke bane pahad', '
Sharbati samandar aur aam ki achaar', '
Dahi hai bemisaal wa ha ha ha, khaaunga peth bharke', '
Saja hai bhojanaalay, bhojan ka hai himaalay', '
Lagi hai bhuk jamake, khaaunga peth bharke', '
Wa ha ha ha,\xa0 wa ha ha ha,\xa0 wa ha ha ha.']
